Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Alegrea Primary School in the Municipality of Marihatag, Province of Surigao Del Sur, to Lingaya Primary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 774
An Act Changing the Name of the Alegrea Primary School in the Municipality of Marihatag, Province of Surigao Del Sur, to Lingaya Primary School
Section 1. The name of the Alegrea Primary School in the Municipality of Marihatag, Province of Surigao del Sur, is changed to Lingaya Primary School.1awphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
